424
00:34:03,200 --> 00:34:06,249
OLSON: Yeah, well,
it's been a long day.

425
00:34:06,280 --> 00:34:10,171
PEREZ: You know,
I heard about that.

426
00:34:10,200 --> 00:34:12,965
